==Charts ==
The piano version of "Love the Way You Lie (Part II)" was not made available to purchase individually, and could only be bought along with the [[iTunes]] edition of the album. However, the version which features [[Eminem]] was available to buy individually.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/loud/id402920935|title=Loud US iTunes |date=2010-11-16|work=[[iTunes Store]]|publisher=([[Apple Inc]])}}</ref> It debuted on [[Canadian Hot 100]] for the week of December&nbsp;4,&nbsp;2010, at number nineteen <ref name="CA">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100?chartDate=2010-12-11&order=gainer#/charts/canadian-hot-100?chartDate=2010-12-04&order=gainer|title=Canada Debut|date=2010-12-04|work=''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]''|publisher=([[Prometheus Global Media]])}}</ref> and stayed on the chart for eight weeks.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/rihanna/658897#/song/rihanna-featuring-eminem/love-the-way-you-lie-part-ii/23091974|title=Canada Debut|date=2011-05-19|work=''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]''|publisher=(Prometheus Global Media)}}</ref> 
